{"id":473611,"date":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":6}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"353","ytitle":"","mtitle":"小分队下乡来","ftitle":"","authors":["俞思林"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"闵行文化馆　俞思林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四舍五村喜传开:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不乘车，不坐船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双腿生风跑着来!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扛起锄头上田坂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大娘村口提意见:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“备好茶水不来吃一碗!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田头就是大舞台，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扔掉镰刀跳起舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放下泥担唱《大寨》。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"针线扁担随身带。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊喂，我家水缸谁挑满?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘿唷，被头帐子洗得雪雪白!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"样样技术好门槛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊喂，我家门窗全修好，”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘿唷，倒塌的墙壁已砌起来!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐坏阿婆、老大爷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“床头拉琴床前唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真是毛主席派的来!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门向着贫农开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏僻村落锣鼓急:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哈，搬来了上海‘大世界’!”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小分队，下乡来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心心相连难舍开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千声万声颂党好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀，永远在咱身边!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"附注:小分队是指各专业剧团组成的、短小精悍的演出队。"}]}